<p>おれはここまで<span class="vocab">考えたら<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>考</rb><rt>かんが</rt></ruby>えたら&nbsp;considered; thought over</span></span>、<span class="vocab">眠くなった<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>眠</rb><rt>ねむ</rt></ruby>くなった&nbsp;grew sleepy</span></span>からぐうぐう<span class="vocab">寝てしまった<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>寝</rb><rt>ね</rt></ruby>てしまった&nbsp;slept</span></span>。<span class="vocab">あくる日<span class="vocabdef">あくる<ruby><rb>日</rb><rt>ひ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;the following day</span></span>は<span class="vocab">思う<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>思</rb><rt>おも</rt></ruby>う&nbsp;thought through; worked out (in one's mind)</span></span><span class="vocab">仔細<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>仔細</rb><rt>しさい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;particulars</span></span>があるから、<span class="vocab">例刻<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>例刻</rb><rt>れいこく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;the usual hour</span></span>より<span class="vocab">早ヤ目に<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>早</rb><rt>は</rt></ruby>ヤ<ruby><rb>目</rb><rt>め</rt></ruby>に&nbsp;early</span></span><span class="vocab">出校して<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出校</rb><rt>しゅっこう</rt></ruby>して&nbsp;appear at the school</span></span><span class="vocab">山嵐<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>山嵐</rb><rt>やまあらし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Yama Arashi (nickname for Hotta, the head mathematics teacher)</span></span>を<span class="vocab">待ち受けた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>待</rb><rt>ま</rt></ruby>ち<ruby><rb>受</rb><rt>う</rt></ruby>けた&nbsp;waited for</span></span>。ところがなかなか<span class="vocab">出て来ない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>で</rt></ruby>て<ruby><rb>来</rb><rt>こ</rt></ruby>ない&nbsp;not appear</span></span>。<span class="vocab">うらなり<span class="vocabdef">うらなり&nbsp;Uranari (nickname for Koga, the English teacher)</span></span>が出て来る。<span class="vocab">漢学<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>漢学</rb><rt>かんがく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Chinese study; classics</span></span>の<span class="vocab">先生<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>先生</rb><rt>せんせい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;teacher</span></span>が出て来る。<span class="vocab">野だ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>野</rb><rt>の</rt></ruby>だ&nbsp;Noda (short for Nodaiko, nickname for Yoshikawa, the art teacher)</span></span>が出て来る。しまいには<span class="vocab">赤シャツ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>赤</rb><rt>あか</rt></ruby>シャツ&nbsp;Red Shirt (nickname for the head teacher)</span></span>まで出て来たが山嵐の<span class="vocab">机<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>机</rb><rt>つくえ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;desk</span></span>の<span class="vocab">上<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>上</rb><rt>うえ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;top (of)</span></span>は<span class="vocab">白墨<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>白墨</rb><rt>はくぼく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;chalk</span></span>が<span class="vocab">一本<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一本</rb><rt>いっぽん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;one (stick)</span></span><span class="vocab">竪<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>竪</rb><rt>たて</rt></ruby>&nbsp;lengthwise</span></span>に<span class="vocab">寝ている<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>寝</rb><rt>ね</rt></ruby>ている&nbsp;lying; resting</span></span>だけで<span class="vocab">閑静<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>閑静</rb><rt>かんせい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;quiet; still</span></span>なものだ。おれは、<span class="vocab">控所<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>控所</rb><rt>ひかえじょ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;staff room</span></span>へはいる<span class="vocab">や否や<span class="vocabdef">や<ruby><rb>否</rb><rt>いな</rt></ruby>や&nbsp;as soon as ...</span></span><span class="vocab">返そう<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>返</rb><rt>かえ</rt></ruby>そう&nbsp;return (something)</span></span>と思って、うちを<span class="vocab">出る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>で</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;leave; depart (from)</span></span><span class="vocab">時<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>時</rb><rt>とき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;time; moment</span></span>から、<span class="vocab">湯銭<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>湯銭</rb><rt>ゆせん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;bath money</span></span>のように<span class="vocab">手の平<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>手</rb><rt>て</rt></ruby>の<ruby><rb>平</rb><rt>ひら</rt></ruby>&nbsp;palm of one's hand</span></span>へ<span class="vocab">入れて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>入</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>れて&nbsp;put into</span></span><span class="vocab">一銭五厘<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一銭五厘</rb><rt>いっせんごりん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;1 sen and 5 rin (0.015 yen)</span></span>、<span class="vocab">学校<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>学校</rb><rt>がっこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;school</span></span>まで<span class="vocab">握って<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>握</rb><rt>にぎ</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;grasp</span></span><span class="vocab">来た<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>来</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>た&nbsp;came (to)</span></span>。おれは<span class="vocab">膏っ手<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>膏</rb><rt>あぶら</rt></ruby>っ<ruby><rb>手</rb><rt>て</rt></ruby>&nbsp;sweaty palms</span></span>だから、<span class="vocab">開けて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>開</rb><rt>あ</rt></ruby>けて&nbsp;open</span></span>みると一銭五厘が<span class="vocab">汗<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>汗</rb><rt>あせ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;sweat</span></span>をかいている。汗をかいてる<span class="vocab">銭<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>銭</rb><rt>ぜに</rt></ruby>&nbsp;money</span></span>を返しちゃ、山嵐が<span class="vocab">何とか<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>何</rb><rt>なん</rt></ruby>とか&nbsp;something</span></span><span class="vocab">云う<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>云</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>う&nbsp;say; remark</span></span>だろうと思ったから、机の上へ<span class="vocab">置いて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>置</rb><rt>お</rt></ruby>いて&nbsp;set; place</span></span>ふうふう<span class="vocab">吹いて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>吹</rb><rt>ふ</rt></ruby>いて&nbsp;blow (on)</span></span>また握った。ところへ赤シャツが来て<span class="vocab">昨日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>昨日</rb><rt>きのう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;yesterday</span></span>は<span class="vocab">失敬<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>失敬</rb><rt>しっけい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;excuse (me); pardon</span></span>、<span class="vocab">迷惑<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>迷惑</rb><rt>めいわく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;unpleasant; annoyance</span></span>でしたろうと云ったから、迷惑じゃありません、<span class="vocab">お蔭で<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>蔭</rb><rt>かげ</rt></ruby>で&nbsp;thanks to; because of</span></span><span class="vocab">腹が減りました<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>腹</rb><rt>はら</rt></ruby>が<ruby><rb>減</rb><rt>へ</rt></ruby>りました&nbsp;worked up an appetite</span></span>と<span class="vocab">答えた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>答</rb><rt>こた</rt></ruby>えた&nbsp;responded</span></span>。すると赤シャツは山嵐の机の上へ<span class="vocab">肱<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>肱</rb><rt>ひじ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;elbow</span></span>を<span class="vocab">突いて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>突</rb><rt>つ</rt></ruby>いて&nbsp;placed; planted against</span></span>、あの<span class="vocab">盤台面<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>盤台面</rb><rt>ばんだいづら</rt></ruby>&nbsp;sauce pan face; large flat face</span></span>をおれの<span class="vocab">鼻<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>鼻</rb><rt>はな</rt></ruby>&nbsp;nose</span></span>の<span class="vocab">側面<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>側面</rb><rt>そくめん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;side (surface)</span></span>へ<span class="vocab">持って来た<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>持</rb><rt>も</rt></ruby>って<ruby><rb>来</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>た&nbsp;brought toward</span></span>から、<span class="vocab">何<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>何</rb><rt>なに</rt></ruby>&nbsp;what</span></span>をするかと思ったら、<span class="vocab">君<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>君</rb><rt>きみ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;you (familiar)</span></span>昨日<span class="vocab">返りがけに<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>返</rb><rt>かえ</rt></ruby>りがけに&nbsp;on the way back</span></span><span class="vocab">船の中<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>船</rb><rt>ふね</rt></ruby>の<ruby><rb>中</rb><rt>なか</rt></ruby>&nbsp;in the boat</span></span>で<span class="vocab">話した<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>話</rb><rt>はな</rt></ruby>した&nbsp;discussed</span></span><span class="vocab">事<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>事</rb><rt>こと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;matters</span></span>は、<span class="vocab">秘密<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>秘密</rb><rt>ひみつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;confidential; secret</span></span>にしてくれたまえ。まだ<span class="vocab">誰にも<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>誰</rb><rt>だれ</rt></ruby>にも&nbsp;(not) to anyone</span></span>話しやしますまいねと云った。<span class="vocab">女<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>女</rb><rt>おんな</rt></ruby>&nbsp;woman; female</span></span>のような<span class="vocab">声<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>声</rb><rt>こえ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;voice</span></span>を<span class="vocab">出す<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>だ</rt></ruby>す&nbsp;put forth; speak (voice)</span></span>だけに<span class="vocab">心配性な<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>心配性</rb><rt>しんぱいせい</rt></ruby>な&nbsp;anxious; uneasy</span></span><span class="vocab">男<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>男</rb><rt>おとこ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;man</span></span>と<span class="vocab">見える<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>見</rb><rt>み</rt></ruby>える&nbsp;appear (as)</span></span>。話さない事はたしかである。しかしこれから話そうと云う<span class="vocab">心持ち<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>心持</rb><rt>こころも</rt></ruby>ち&nbsp;feeling; intent</span></span>で、すでに一銭五厘手の平に<span class="vocab">用意<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>用意</rb><rt>ようい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;preparation</span></span>しているくらいだから、ここで赤シャツから<span class="vocab">口留め<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>口留</rb><rt>くちど</rt></ruby>め&nbsp;silencing; gagging</span></span>をされちゃ、ちと<span class="vocab">困る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>困</rb><rt>こま</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;be troubled; take issue (with something)</span></span>。赤シャツも赤シャツだ。山嵐と<span class="vocab">名を指さない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>名</rb><rt>な</rt></ruby>を<ruby><rb>指</rb><rt>さ</rt></ruby>さない&nbsp;call out by name</span></span>にしろ、あれほど<span class="vocab">推察<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>推察</rb><rt>すいさつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;conjecture; inference</span></span>の<span class="vocab">出来る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出来</rb><rt>でき</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;can do (something)</span></span><span class="vocab">謎<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>謎</rb><rt>なぞ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;riddle; puzzle; nuances</span></span>をかけておきながら、<span class="vocab">今さら<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>今</rb><rt>いま</rt></ruby>さら&nbsp;at this (belated) point</span></span>その謎を<span class="vocab">解いちゃ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>解</rb><rt>と</rt></ruby>いちゃ&nbsp;solve; unravel</span></span><span class="vocab">迷惑<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>迷惑</rb><rt>めいわく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;inconvenience; trouble</span></span>だとは<span class="vocab">教頭<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>教頭</rb><rt>きょうとう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;head teacher</span></span>とも思えぬ<span class="vocab">無責任<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>無責任</rb><rt>むせきにん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;irresponsible</span></span>だ。<span class="vocab">元来<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>元来</rb><rt>がんらい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;fundamentally; essentially</span></span>ならおれが山嵐と<span class="vocab">戦争<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>戦争</rb><rt>せんそう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;hostilities; combat</span></span>をはじめて<span class="vocab">鎬を削ってる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>鎬</rb><rt>しのぎ</rt></ruby>を<ruby><rb>削</rb><rt>けず</rt></ruby>ってる&nbsp;fighting furiously</span></span><span class="vocab">真中<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>真中</rb><rt>まんなか</rt></ruby>&nbsp;middle of</span></span>へ<span class="vocab">出て<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>で</rt></ruby>て&nbsp;appear; make one's entrance</span></span><span class="vocab">堂々と<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>堂々</rb><rt>どうどう</rt></ruby>と&nbsp;boldly; brazenly</span></span>おれの<span class="vocab">肩を持つ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>肩</rb><rt>かた</rt></ruby>を<ruby><rb>持</rb><rt>も</rt></ruby>つ&nbsp;support; take a person's side</span></span>べきだ。それでこそ<span class="vocab">一校<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一校</rb><rt>いっこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;our school</span></span>の教頭で、赤シャツを<span class="vocab">着ている<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>着</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>ている&nbsp;wear</span></span><span class="vocab">主意も立つ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>主意</rb><rt>ちゅうい</rt></ruby>も<ruby><rb>立</rb><rt>た</rt></ruby>つ&nbsp;make worthy of attention</span></span>というもんだ。</p>

