<p>おれはこう<span class="vocab">考えて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>考</rb><rt>かんが</rt></ruby>えて&nbsp;considered; thought</span></span><span class="vocab">何か<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>何</rb><rt>なに</rt></ruby>か&nbsp;something</span></span><span class="vocab">云おう<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>云</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>おう&nbsp;say; speak</span></span>かなと考えてみたが、云うなら<span class="vocab">人<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>人</rb><rt>ひと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;people; everyone</span></span>を<span class="vocab">驚ろかす<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>驚</rb><rt>おど</rt></ruby>ろかす&nbsp;astonish; impress</span></span>ように<span class="vocab">滔々と述べたてなくっちゃつまらない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>滔々</rb><rt>とうとう</rt></ruby>と<ruby><rb>述</rb><rt>の</rt></ruby>べたてなくっちゃつまらない&nbsp;must be stated with great eloquence</span></span>、おれの<span class="vocab">癖<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>癖</rb><rt>くせ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;habit; mannerism</span></span>として、<span class="vocab">腹が立った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>腹</rb><rt>はら</rt></ruby>が<ruby><rb>立</rb><rt>た</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;become angry; be riled up</span></span>ときに<span class="vocab">口をきく<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>口</rb><rt>くち</rt></ruby>をきく&nbsp;speak</span></span>と、<span class="vocab">二言か三言<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>二言</rb><rt>ふたこと</rt></ruby>か<ruby><rb>三言</rb><rt>みこと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;two or three words</span></span>で<span class="vocab">必ず<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>必</rb><rt>かなら</rt></ruby>ず&nbsp;without fail</span></span><span class="vocab">行き塞って<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>行</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>き<ruby><rb>塞</rb><rt>つま</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;get tongue tied; be at a loss for words</span></span>しまう。<span class="vocab">狸<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>狸</rb><rt>たぬき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Tanuki (nickname for the school principal)</span></span>でも<span class="vocab">赤シャツ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>赤</rb><rt>あか</rt></ruby>シャツ&nbsp;Red Shirt (nickname for the head teacher)</span></span>でも<span class="vocab">人物<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>人物</rb><rt>じんぶつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;character; personal integrity</span></span>から云うと、おれよりも<span class="vocab">下等<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>下等</rb><rt>かとう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;inferior; vulgar</span></span>だが、<span class="vocab">弁舌<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>弁舌</rb><rt>べんぜつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;speech; eloquence</span></span>はなかなか<span class="vocab">達者<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>達者</rb><rt>たっしゃ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;skilled; proficient</span></span>だから、まずい<span class="vocab">事<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>事</rb><rt>こと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;content; things</span></span>を<span class="vocab">喋舌って<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>喋舌</rb><rt>しゃべ</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;say; utter</span></span><span class="vocab">揚足を取られちゃ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>揚足</rb><rt>あげあし</rt></ruby>を<ruby><rb>取</rb><rt>と</rt></ruby>られちゃ&nbsp;be tripped up on one's own words</span></span><span class="vocab">面白くない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>面白</rb><rt>おもしろ</rt></ruby>くない&nbsp;not good; unpleasant</span></span>。ちょっと<span class="vocab">腹案<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>腹案</rb><rt>ふくあん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;preparation; outline (of a speech)</span></span>を<span class="vocab">作って<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>作</rb><rt>つく</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;make; craft</span></span>みようと、<span class="vocab">胸<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>胸</rb><rt>むね</rt></ruby>&nbsp;one's heart; one's mind</span></span>のなかで<span class="vocab">文章<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>文章</rb><rt>ぶんしょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;words; composition</span></span>を作ってる。すると<span class="vocab">前<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>前</rb><rt>まえ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;in front (of)</span></span>に<span class="vocab">居た<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>居</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>た&nbsp;was (in a place)</span></span><span class="vocab">野だ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>野</rb><rt>の</rt></ruby>だ&nbsp;Noda (short for Nodaiko, nickname for Yoshikawa, the art teacher)</span></span>が<span class="vocab">突然<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>突然</rb><rt>とつぜん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;suddenly</span></span><span class="vocab">起立した<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>起立</rb><rt>きりつ</rt></ruby>した&nbsp;stood up</span></span>には驚ろいた。野だの癖に<span class="vocab">意見<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>意見</rb><rt>いけん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;opinion</span></span>を<span class="vocab">述べる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>述</rb><rt>の</rt></ruby>べる&nbsp;speak; comment</span></span>なんて<span class="vocab">生意気<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>生意気</rb><rt>なまいき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;presumptuous</span></span>だ。野だは<span class="vocab">例の<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>例</rb><rt>れい</rt></ruby>の&nbsp;usual; characteristic</span></span><span class="vocab">へらへら調<span class="vocabdef">へらへら<ruby><rb>調</rb><rt>ちょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;flippant tone; air of superficiality</span></span>で「<span class="vocab">実に<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>実</rb><rt>じつ</rt></ruby>に&nbsp;in fact; to tell the truth</span></span><span class="vocab">今回<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>今回</rb><rt>こんかい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;this time</span></span>の<span class="vocab">バッタ<span class="vocabdef">バッタ&nbsp;grasshopper</span></span><span class="vocab">事件<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>事件</rb><rt>じけん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;incident</span></span><span class="vocab">及び<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>及</rb><rt>およ</rt></ruby>び&nbsp;and</span></span><span class="vocab">咄喊<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>咄喊</rb><rt>とっかん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;shouting; battle cry</span></span>事件は<span class="vocab">吾々<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>吾々</rb><rt>われわれ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;we</span></span><span class="vocab">心ある<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>心</rb><rt>こころ</rt></ruby>ある&nbsp;concerned</span></span><span class="vocab">職員<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>職員</rb><rt>しょくいん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;staff</span></span>をして、ひそかに<span class="vocab">吾校<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>吾校</rb><rt>わがこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;our school</span></span><span class="vocab">将来<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>将来</rb><rt>しょうらい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;future</span></span>の<span class="vocab">前途<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>前途</rb><rt>ぜんと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;prospects; possibilities</span></span>に<span class="vocab">危惧<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>危惧</rb><rt>きぐ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;fear; misgivings</span></span>の<span class="vocab">念<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>念</rb><rt>ねん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;sense; feeling</span></span>を<span class="vocab">抱かしむる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>抱</rb><rt>いだ</rt></ruby>かしむる&nbsp;can cause one to harbor (doubt or fear)</span></span><span class="vocab">に足る<span class="vocabdef">に<ruby><rb>足</rb><rt>た</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;be sufficient to</span></span><span class="vocab">珍事<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>珍事</rb><rt>ちんじ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;rare event; singular incident</span></span>でありまして、吾々職員たるものはこの<span class="vocab">際<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>際</rb><rt>さい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;occasion</span></span><span class="vocab">奮って<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>奮</rb><rt>ふる</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;energetically; of one's own accord</span></span><span class="vocab">自ら<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>自</rb><rt>みずか</rt></ruby>ら&nbsp;personally</span></span><span class="vocab">省りみて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>省</rb><rt>かえ</rt></ruby>りみて&nbsp;reflect upon; take notice of</span></span>、<span class="vocab">全校<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>全校</rb><rt>ぜんこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;the entire school</span></span>の<span class="vocab">風紀<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>風紀</rb><rt>ふうき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;discipline; public morals</span></span>を<span class="vocab">振粛<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>振粛</rb><rt>しんしゅく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;strict enforcement</span></span>しなければなりません。それで<span class="vocab">ただ今<span class="vocabdef">ただ<ruby><rb>今</rb><rt>いま</rt></ruby>&nbsp;just now</span></span><span class="vocab">校長<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>校長</rb><rt>こうちょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;school principal</span></span>及び<span class="vocab">教頭<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>教頭</rb><rt>きょうとう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;head teacher</span></span>のお述べになった<span class="vocab">お説<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>説</rb><rt>せつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;opinion; remarks</span></span>は、実に<span class="vocab">肯綮に中った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>肯綮</rb><rt>こうけい</rt></ruby>に<ruby><rb>中</rb><rt>あた</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;hit the mark; strike the right chord</span></span><span class="vocab">剴切な<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>剴切</rb><rt>がいせつ</rt></ruby>な&nbsp;appropriate; relevant (to the case)</span></span><span class="vocab">お考え<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>考</rb><rt>かんが</rt></ruby>え&nbsp;thought; consideration</span></span>で<span class="vocab">私<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>私</rb><rt>わたし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;I</span></span>は<span class="vocab">徹頭徹尾<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>徹頭徹尾</rb><rt>てっとうてつび</rt></ruby>&nbsp;thoroughly; to the core</span></span><span class="vocab">賛成致します<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>賛成</rb><rt>さんせい</rt></ruby><ruby><rb>致</rb><rt>いた</rt></ruby>します&nbsp;humbly agree</span></span>。どうかなるべく<span class="vocab">寛大の<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>寛大</rb><rt>かんだい</rt></ruby>の&nbsp;lenient; tolerant</span></span><span class="vocab">ご処分<span class="vocabdef">ご<ruby><rb>処分</rb><rt>しょぶん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;dealing (with); punishment</span></span>を<span class="vocab">仰ぎたいと思います<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>仰</rb><rt>あお</rt></ruby>ぎたいと<ruby><rb>思</rb><rt>おも</rt></ruby>います&nbsp;would like to request</span></span>」と云った。野だの云う事は<span class="vocab">言語<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>言語</rb><rt>ことば</rt></ruby>&nbsp;words</span></span>はあるが<span class="vocab">意味<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>意味</rb><rt>いみ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;meaning</span></span>がない、<span class="vocab">漢語<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>漢語</rb><rt>かんご</rt></ruby>&nbsp;big words; difficult words</span></span>を<span class="vocab">のべつに<span class="vocabdef">のべつに&nbsp;without pause</span></span><span class="vocab">陳列する<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>陳列</rb><rt>ちんれつ</rt></ruby>する&nbsp;put on display; make a show of</span></span>ぎりで<span class="vocab">訳が分らない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>訳</rb><rt>わけ</rt></ruby>が<ruby><rb>分</rb><rt>わか</rt></ruby>らない&nbsp;have no idea what something or someone means</span></span>。<span class="vocab">分った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>分</rb><rt>わか</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;understood</span></span>のは徹頭徹尾賛成致しますと云う言葉だけだ。</p>

